  "title": "Pigeonpea in eastern and southern Africa: summary proceedings of the Launching Meeting for the African Development Bank/ICRISAT Collaborative Pigeonpea Project for Eastern and Southern Africa, Nairobi, Kenya, 17-18 Mar 1992 and Lilongwe, Malawi, 30-31 Mar 1992",
